RAServer.scala: resource allocation servers (two versions), plus testing code.

PartialRAServer.scala: partial resource allocation server, which buffers
requests that cannot be served immediately.

Exchanger.scala: an exchanger, plus testing code.

FilterChan.scala: A filter channel.

MenWomen.scala: The men and women problem. (Exercise)

AtomicBroadcast.scala: Atomic broadcast object (Exercise).